}
```

This program is supposed to print the sum of all five elements but prints the wrong value. What is the bug?

```cpp
#include <iostream>

int main() {
    int data[5]{ 1, 2, 3, 4, 5 };
    int sum = 0;
    for (int i = 0; i <= 5; ++i)
        sum += data[i];
    std::cout << sum << '\n';
}
```
